&quot;Apparently, Webster agrees with me. The name says it all!&quot;<br>
And us, and Trish and Candy and Heather....We all agreed that in YOUR theology he is the enemy of god, but then prejudging a belief system before studying it would be like a JW refusing to study LDS because it is of Satan right? Are you seeing what we mean by hypocrisy here?<br>
<br>
&quot;Do any of you really think that the name was not created to signify that they oppose basic Judeo Christian values and or doctrine?&quot;<br>
<br>
So? How does this change the argument? Piss you off as a xian? So? Values in opposition to intolerance, sexism, violence against innocents doesn't sound so bad to me...see how perspective is everything?<br>
<br>
